{"tid":436208,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"[C]malloc有咩唔好?","createTime":"2017-10-15T03:25:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-31T06:20:58.000Z","uid":65030,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"59fcff0de8976b8de0cbddac8cc72ef1710114a9","tid":436208,"uid":65030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T03:25:56.000Z","msg":"D人成日話malloc好多缺點, 咁有咩缺點,<br />\n如果係, 唔用malloc可以點做"},{"pid":"9277125686c610793a69b42a1fb2327f5bbd3e9b","tid":436208,"uid":38316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T03:43:59.000Z","msg":"你寫embedded system?<br />\n唔係既OS level program你唔用malloc有咩選擇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48f3535c55f92a11f1cb02ae2fc81ca529240493","tid":436208,"uid":65030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T04:00:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你寫embedded system?<br />\n唔係既OS level program你唔用malloc有咩選擇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但係d 人成日話避免使用malloc"},{"pid":"142fc6c087dfabb7ea5ab94b810590feacab28f3","tid":436208,"uid":41887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T04:45:11.000Z","msg":"自己寫個memory pool，如果唔係有咩選擇？"},{"pid":"3971dba745edf607a1ce0fe52ed73f298eba5f27","tid":436208,"uid":105553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T05:21:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>自己寫個memory pool，如果唔係有咩選擇？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n要睇object嘅scope同size，例如可以用mmap，sbrk。function scope可以用alloca。自己寫memory allocator亦可以。"},{"pid":"185b4f8a138615cc17eddf88c6766714cff8e977","tid":436208,"uid":105553,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T05:24:55.000Z","msg":"BTW, 最霸氣嘅memory management strategy，不過大部份應用都唔適用呢個方法。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://groups.google.com/forum/message/raw?msg=comp.lang.ada/E9bNCvDQ12k/1tezW24ZxdAJ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgroups.google.com%2Fforum%2Fmessage%2Fraw%3Fmsg%3Dcomp.lang.ada%2FE9bNCvDQ12k%2F1tezW24ZxdAJ&d=4j05Xm5bLBYU9Xs%2FN1sKw%2FM6KyiA14vjm6WlJCMZo68%3D&h=f98765f6\" target=\"_blank\">https://groups.google.com/forum/message/raw?msg=comp.lang.ada/E9bNCvDQ12k/1tezW24ZxdAJ</a>"},{"pid":"0ed93ea09376ea6cf09e59fbc8efcb3ae42af53d","tid":436208,"uid":63156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T05:51:28.000Z","msg":"點解要avoid malloc<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n所有dynamic memory allocation都係個兩個問題:<br />\nmemory fragmentation<br />\nmemory leak<br />\n<br />\n如果要完全避免呢兩個問題就完全唔好用dynamic memory用返stack囉<br />\n<br />\n最重要係知道點樣用同幾時應該用幾時唔應該用啫<br />\n唔通又要好似goto咁咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5e331ff244e9644edc21d217f4acaadc5f9f54d","tid":436208,"uid":115197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T13:34:49.000Z","msg":"手尾好啲就唔會有memory leak <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d0a9d0c2933ec5ad31ed8019c908eaf3a389785","tid":436208,"uid":148531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T06:20:58.000Z","msg":"malloc有乜撚野唔好。。。你係指malloc嘅implementation?<br />\n<br />\ntcmalloc jemalloc呢啲？"}]}